{"tid":2348709,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：涉國安法保釋　辯方需證明被告不會再犯「國安法」","createTime":"2021-01-01T03:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T05:09:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a1b37000aee3ef4d038e4e5752d33dcc4625c642","tid":2348709,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"終審法院批准律政司就壹傳媒創辦人黎智英保釋案提出的上訴許可，黎智英需即時還押至2月初再訊。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊表示，一般刑事案件法庭在考慮是否批准被告保釋時，主要考慮被告會否有機會棄保潛逃，干擾證人或銷毁證據及會否再犯，但涉及香港國安法的案件，就涉及多一個要求，就是法庭要信納被告保釋期間不會再犯香港國安法，而有關舉證責任就由控方轉移到辯方。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊在本台節目千禧年代表示，根據港區國安法41條，列明檢控要由律政司書面同意，但不影響犯罪嫌疑人申請保釋，即是犯了國安法的人，並非一定不可保釋。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，不同意涉及國安法的案件，被告人的保釋機會被削弱，而是門檻有所提升。"},{"pid":"e0f613d390474dbbb73bbf029ecfc730b7cc99f3","tid":2348709,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:12:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568152-20210101.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568152-20210101.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindha%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=9f0d1e3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568152-20210101.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=411ccddd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568152-20210101.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ab7a4b8ba296a304760f0c09622587dfca808e58","tid":2348709,"uid":39710,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:12:55.000Z","msg":"低鳩能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23dbc2309d2a3a1f141fc2c60f29dc2943f956e0","tid":2348709,"uid":284855,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:13:14.000Z","msg":"只有死人先可保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"